{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act3d0_level_act3d0_05_end","storyGroup":"act3d0","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act3d0_level_act3d0_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"OF-5","storyName":"别阻止我","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"黑和锡兰的交谈还在继续。\n不过这一次，黑理解了锡兰的坚持，也发现了自己遭受蒙骗。\n\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act3d0/level_act3d0_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"a003_05","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["锡兰","黑"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第六关（后）","id":0},{"type":"Background","id":1},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":2,"musicid":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Character","id":5},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_Festival_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#5","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"1","id":8},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"黑，我在维多利亚留学这么多年，并不是在虚度光阴。","id":9,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我在那里学习了与天灾和源石有关的，最先进的科学技术。","id":10,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"对你来说或许是天方夜谭的事，对我来说却是理所当然并且正在发生的事。","id":11,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我所学习的知识，我所信奉的理论，它们都在告诉我我的判断是正确的。","id":12,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#5","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"2","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"小姐你学的并不是法学。","id":14,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#5","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"嗯......？","id":16,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#2","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"2","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"罗德岛在市政厅做什么？","id":18,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#2","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"搜集克洛宁的罪证。","id":20,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#2","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"2","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"嗯？","id":22,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#2","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"克洛宁也许很坏，却没有那么蠢。","id":24,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"作为天灾信使他不可能不知道现在火山的状况有问题。","id":25,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"他一定是因为自己的盘算才掩盖事实的，只要暗暗搜集他的罪证......","id":26,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#2","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"2","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"我认为罗德岛和他会正面冲突，所谓暗中搜集证据，不可能成功。","id":28,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#2","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......","id":30,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"没，没关系！只要你不在就......","id":31,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#8"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"小姐，我想知道你为什么要这么做。如果我能得到一个合理的答案，我不会追究罗德岛。","id":33,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"......我必须这么做。我不相信父亲是无血无肉的人，他绝对不会看着这种事情发生。","id":35,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"父亲爱着这个城市，比谁都爱，没有人比我更清楚这一点了。","id":36,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#3","focus":"2","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"你还恨他吗？","id":38,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#9","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#3","focus":"1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"为什么？如果该恨的话，应该是父亲恨我，因为我的出生带走了母亲......","id":40,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#9"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"但他从来没有这么做。","id":41,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#9"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我只是讨厌他不肯把事情说出来，把所有事情全都安排好。","id":42,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#9"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"看起来好像是在保护我，实际上却害得我什么都不知道，什么都做不了。","id":43,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#9"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#3","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"就连这次也一样！一定是克洛宁蒙骗了父亲，让他对火山爆发的事情完全不知情。","id":45,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"所以父亲才会让克洛宁阻止我发布报告！这不叫恨吧？","id":46,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"2","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"火山爆发？","id":48,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"克洛宁说的是，小姐准备把老爷过去的机密事件全部抖露，让老爷退职，接受审判。","id":49,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"啊？不，我父亲过去做了些什么？","id":51,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#8"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#8","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#5","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"不，没什么。","id":53,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"......唔，原来是这样，我知道了。","id":54,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#5","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"所以克洛宁也不是因为父亲的命令才阻拦我的。呼，我也差不多明白了。","id":56,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"黑，如果真是那种事，我会请求更具备法律效力的渠道。","id":57,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"我所做的自然也是为了这个城市，为了我的故乡。","id":58,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#3","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"我明白了。小姐并不在乎过去的事情，也不在乎所谓的名誉。","id":60,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"我和小姐一样，老爷也一样。","id":61,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#5","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"呼。不管别人怎么猜想，我选择相信你，相信父亲。","id":63,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"即使是目的产生了冲突，我也知道，这是我们两个人之间的事。","id":64,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"所以我相信，和我一样了解这个城市的你，一定会知道我会在这里。","id":65,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"这样，你就会亲自来阻止我。","id":66,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#4","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"说起来，市长是谁都无所谓吧？父亲也一定会这么觉得。他在乎的，不也是这个城市吗？","id":68,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"所以，父亲一定会同意我的观点的。","id":69,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"锡兰","text":"黑......我说的对吗？","id":70,"figure":"char_348_ceylon_4#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_348_ceylon_4#4","name2":"char_340_shwaz_2#5","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑","text":"你长大了，小姐。","id":72,"figure":"char_340_shwaz_2#5"},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":73},{"type":"Dialog","id":74},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"Image","id":76}],"characters":["锡兰","黑"]}